name: Bop Cat
description: Bop cat is a meme coin on SOL centered around creating a fun and engaging community-driven ecosystem. Bop cat was created by the popular artist RareDoodle. Crypto enthusiasts have created an exciting community centered around rare doodles creation “bop cat” with the intentions to bring entertainment and classic memes back to crypto. The cat is widely known for the way it bops up and down in your wallet and on DEX.
